3) Why I chose this CD (and why I rejected the alternatives)
- Choice justification: Overall, I selected the Roxette greatest‑hits CD because several of my highest priorities are satisfied: the mixes are midrange‑forward with vocals kept front and present (which I repeatedly emphasized), the arrangements are melody‑first and richly layered with lush backing harmonies, and the sequencing is cohesive and rewards front‑to‑back listening. Those are significant positives for a listener who prizes a strong vocal center, clear instrument separation in the midrange, and rewarding sequencing — all explicit in my self‑introduction.
